For those who don't know...

1. Use WinRAR to extract

2. Burn or mount (I use Daemon Tools to mount)

3. Install the game, but DON'T RUN IT YET!!

4. OPEN the CD (if using Daemon Tools) and go into the "CRACK" folder and copy "RCT3" file. Then paste it in your program files folder where the game has been installed. This will replace the "RCT3" file that's already there.

5. NOW you can run it!
